<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/register.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <title>Register</title>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
   <h1 class="logo">DaleWears<p class="easy">...making you comfy</p></h1>
 </nav>
 <div class="main">
     <div class="container">
    <h3>Welcome to DaleWears!</h3>
    <h4>Thank you for joining the Dalewears family! We are thrilled to have you here. As a member of our community, you will enjoy an exclusive shopping experience tailored just for you.<br><br>
        At Dalewears, we are passionate about providing you with the latest in fashion trends, premium quality clothing, and exceptional customer service. Our collection features a wide range of stylish and comfortable apparel, designed to help you express your unique personality and style.<br><br>By registering with us, you gain access to:<br><br>
        Exclusive Discounts: Enjoy special offers and discounts available only to our registered members.
        Personalized Recommendations: Receive tailored fashion recommendations based on your preferences.
        Effortless Shopping: Save your favorite items, manage your orders, and track your purchases easily.<br></h4>
 <h4>We are committed to ensuring your shopping experience with us is seamless and enjoyable. If you have any <br>questions or need assistance, our customer service team is always here to help.<br><br></h4>
 <h3>Welcome aboard, and happy shopping!!!</h3>
 </div>

    <div class="register-container">
        <div class="form-section">
            <h2>Sign Up</h2>
            <form action="/register" method="post">
                <label for="username">Username:</label>
                <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>
                
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                
                <div class="password-container">
                    <label for="password">Password:</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
                    <i class="toggle-password" onclick="togglePasswordVisibility()" id="togglePassword"></i>
                </div>
                
                <div class="checkbox">
                    <input type="Checkbox"><span>I agreed with the terms and conditions applied</span>
                    </div>

                <button type="submit">Click to Register</button>
            </form>
            <p class="terms"> By Clicking the sign up button, you agree to our <br> <a href="/policy">Terms and Condition</a> and  <a href="/policy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
            <p class="already">Already have an account? <a href="/login">Login Here</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    
    <script>
        function togglePasswordVisibility() {
            const passwordField = document.getElementById('password');
            const toggleIcon = document.getElementById('togglePassword');
    
            if (passwordField.type === 'password') {
                passwordField.type = 'text';
                toggleIcon.classList.add('show-password');
            } else {
                passwordField.type = 'password';
                toggleIcon.classList.remove('show-password');
            }
        }
    </script>
    
    
</body>
</html>

